data.enText: to make a process happen more quickly
We have developed rapid order processing to expedite deliveries to customers.
data.chText: 我们已创造了快速处理订单的方法以便迅速将货物送达顾客。

example: I will try to expedite the matter

example.ex: The government has been extremely reluctant to expedite investigations that might result in his trial...
example.tran: 当局极不情愿推进调查，因为其结果可能会让他接受审判。

example.ex: We tried to help you expedite your plans.
example.tran: 我们尽力帮你加快实现你的计划。

value.def: If you expedite something, you cause it to be done more quickly.
